{"tid":662083,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[HKU] 工學院 聯手 醫學院 打造最強學科！JS6925！！！","createTime":"2018-05-12T06:26:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-17T20:18:26.000Z","uid":14170,"like":2,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"065392274f0d9349f96a2ef49c297e40018fc308","tid":662083,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T06:26:20.000Z","msg":"【重要更新：新課程 JS6925 工學學士(生物醫學工程) 有意報讀的學生可免費改選】<br />\n原屬 #JS6963 #工學學士 內的 #生物醫學工程 主修將分成獨立課程：#JS6925 -工學學士(生物醫學工程) ( [BENG(BME)]。相關考生可在5月17日23:59前在聯招系統進行一次免費改選。詳情請參閱：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2IeBZAh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2IeBZAh&d=0GBvpCFIhN75uPy7XBKWkZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=b33c0201\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2IeBZAh</a><br />\n<br />\nBENG(BME) 由香港大學工程學院及李嘉誠醫學院合辦，培養學生跨學科的技能，包括基本科學、數學、工程和生命科學，涵蓋廣泛的現代生物醫學工程學科與生物醫學工程相關的體驗學習機會。全面的訓練讓學生學習如何運用工程學原理來改善醫療和促進生物醫學研究，並於健康相關的議題上建立專業、道德和社會責任。<br />\n想深入了解 JS6925 BENG(BME)的收生準則及課程架構，請報名參加工程學院入學講座(15/5): <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2FE8F3T\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2FE8F3T&d=0GBvpCFIhN75uPy7XBKWkZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=6b20f64e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2FE8F3T</a>"},{"pid":"b9672e0776876a33c3dc9ab46711b6ca609dc827","tid":662083,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T06:30:27.000Z","msg":"前身係由港大工學院開辦既 Medical Engineering，依家醫學院都加入埋一份 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/12/143017_110b7c1c5be5e0f3b355fe1faf90a287.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F12%2F143017_110b7c1c5be5e0f3b355fe1faf90a287.png&h=211cd560&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"97b9685327ac3b690b4afcd79cdf2944d55354dc","tid":662083,"uid":34525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T06:31:08.000Z","msg":"Jed"},{"pid":"47274ca9e72281e6e